{"tid":1520673,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"831西環不了 流水延長戰利市民 陣地快速戰利政府","createTime":"2019-08-31T02:24:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T12:19:01.000Z","uid":186,"like":139,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"bba2bda4a7c90136d8422432ceabc3fb6412d47e","tid":1520673,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:24:04.000Z","msg":"政府目標得一個 盡快清場<br />\n政府琴日已經按捺不住 要拉一班立法會議員<br />\n目標係引示威者All In<br />\n<br />\n參考返2014年11月30日<br />\n雨傘end game 主動送頭<br />\n最後士氣一沉不起<br />\n今日831 大量風向吹緊一家要去西環<br />\n老老豆豆 去琴西環就贏咩<br />\n要做 香港大把地方要做<br />\n<br />\n總之 唔好去西環<br />\n<br />\n「雨傘革命之學聯升級」發生於2014年11月30日，學民思潮及學聯宣布希望包圍政府總部阻礙政府運作，以將行動升級。示威者與警方星夜於龍和道一帶展開攻防戰，惟至早上節節敗退，警方一度攻至海富中心港鐵站口，是佔領局勢穩定以來警方最接近金鐘佔領區核心的一次。學聯升級行動全面失敗，更有大量市民受傷，網民對相關策略及警方的舉動議論紛紛。"},{"pid":"dffc506fcb1f6e7c56f8d4a5e0814a3653f7756f","tid":1520673,"uid":33930,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:24:17.000Z","msg":"幾句講哂<br />\n831宗教集會 港島見<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">901 1點鐘 機場見</span></span><br />\n92大三罷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OvNBCkd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOvNBCkd.jpg&h=f0ee9ddd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">記住啊 我地只係幫機管局做交通壓力測試</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2SPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=df79dee5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 公海</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2SPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=b6798b49\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">901 機場 宣傳</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2SPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=4179668c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">三罷 Channel</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><a href=\"http://T.me/hkgeneralstrike9293\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FT.me%2Fhkgeneralstrike9293&d=7zzHsEpI0SCc5dEpMOtc2SPhHSzXeBMEaaQhzK3ZYsY%3D&h=10a23119\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">T.me/hkgeneralstrike9293</a></span>"},{"pid":"fb5cb329a3f6cafaa4ee7067e6cdb9d7dbf3505c","tid":1520673,"uid":186,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:24:51.000Z","msg":"Be water 精神 係 唔會知你去邊<br />\n封哂西環引你地去"},{"pid":"3a952bf75920e88d248573a2cc569623ec4d83a3","tid":1520673,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:48:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8387302afcb495004d8d763fd0cde72c69890dfa","tid":1520673,"uid":139294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:48:32.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"1b10587f031ae64d1d3464b535ad885c59da8927","tid":1520673,"uid":103057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:49:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b07ff1e2ef4c07f37543c17c2bddf5a17645d1f","tid":1520673,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:49:49.000Z","msg":"不要141130 <br />\n送頭啊"},{"pid":"fbbef07b8aa78c6b77f53f80f99c80652f8bb697","tid":1520673,"uid":186,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:50:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/xM-sjRgNqLM/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FxM-sjRgNqLM%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=d988e506&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"183f7acb87a52db6b0867bd31862b32fe07d38da","tid":1520673,"uid":186,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:50:48.000Z","msg":"劇本黎<br />\n<img src=\"https://canview.rfaweb.org/cantonese/commentaries/tym/com-10062016082138.html/com-quote620.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcanview.rfaweb.org%2Fcantonese%2Fcommentaries%2Ftym%2Fcom-10062016082138.html%2Fcom-quote620.jpg&h=59101739&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"997458459c0b93b7d565485201a639eeb45c0a3e","tid":1520673,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:51:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9d0f0a3d864893d0d92fdbb8ff0b628651dff2c","tid":1520673,"uid":186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:51:29.000Z","msg":"2014年11月29日，學民思潮及學聯突然在facebook專頁宣布在金鐘佔領區舉行集會，但只着支持者於11月30日下午6時前到達，未有詳情。網民紛紛流傳有關訊息，並指「信埋學聯最後一次」。<br />\n<br />\n11月30日，金鐘佔領區於下午6時開始集會；晚上9時，雙學宣布「雨傘運動」升級，計劃包圍政總。開始學聯在集會中，宣布將運動升級，前往包圍禮賓府。其後示威者重新佔領龍和道，與警方爆發衝突。過千名示威者沿添美道向龍和道進發，約10時50分龍和道隧道已完全由示威者堵塞，11時學聯表示已包圍政總，呼籲示威者留守。<br />\n<br />\n最高峰時近5,000示威者參與，但警方亟欲重開龍和道，通宵與示威者爆發了四場攻防戰。示威者曾兩度佔領政總外的龍和道，當中大部份都是赤手空拳，只有少數人配備了簡單的頭盔及盾牌自衞，及隨手找來鐵馬及垃圾桶做防線。相反警方以警棍、胡椒噴霧、催淚水劑與水炮鎮壓，民眾堅守12小時後最終節節敗退，有大量市民受傷，警方更一度順勢循添馬公園及政府總部行人天橋攻至海富中心港鐵站口，是佔領局勢穩定以來警方最接近金鐘佔領區核心的一次。"},{"pid":"dce446e6ae53b6ebfbc713d8462a385b3e73a551","tid":1520673,"uid":186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:52:26.000Z","msg":"12月1日晚，雙學承認行動失敗，學民思潮黃之鋒等三子宣布無限期絕食抗爭。晚上集會，有示威者衝上大台責難，質疑佔中糾察隊及民陣警權關注組召集人陳樹暉在衝突中並無現身，並要求與雙學當面對質，希望對方解釋行動失敗原因，又指責當晚人數並不足夠包圍政總，導致數名救援隊成員受傷，「傷嘅傷、拉嘅拉」。"},{"pid":"f9b55c9f58e79f4c2ec773d272960668888462a9","tid":1520673,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:52:43.000Z","msg":"831 西環以外"},{"pid":"5c9da35387e2dd44f075773f38c83b3d8ace198d","tid":1520673,"uid":134744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:52:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"04bb9624bf0c730f4ed4433250d1635c0fc8948d","tid":1520673,"uid":34773,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:53:10.000Z","msg":"總之集完會走佬不送頭。 明天和平練春袋"},{"pid":"e2dcc351ca66aca12ba53e58d58f9efc8d01f241","tid":1520673,"uid":84113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:53:51.000Z","msg":"推！"},{"pid":"1584d919f5e7e9c944c4803700509d93adaf2cd5","tid":1520673,"uid":84113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:54:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5be04c8fc766b5063627b1580a4b409ce0c9d394","tid":1520673,"uid":3776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:54:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"54148c15a6dcb6aa360bd0d4996fcb942667a9b2","tid":1520673,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:54:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>To 港島玩pokemon go</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"3adf23ab632f829ad5585862476e5cdf1ad54aa5","tid":1520673,"uid":7119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:55:36.000Z","msg":"Agree，西環真係送頭"},{"pid":"07f2c0120d9525023ab07337268d2e1c2726e577","tid":1520673,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:59:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2237bb8f9b6dc2956c0c74574d8dc739308adf7b","tid":1520673,"uid":276440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d9d0f0a3d864893d0d92fdbb8ff0b628651dff2c","tid":1520673,"uid":186,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:51:29.000Z","msg":"2014年11月29日，學民思潮及學聯突然在facebook專頁宣布在金鐘佔領區舉行集會，但只着支持者於11月30日下午6時前到達，未有詳情。網民紛紛流傳有關訊息，並指「信埋學聯最後一次」。<br />\n<br />\n11月30日，金鐘佔領區於下午6時開始集會；晚上9時，雙學宣布「雨傘運動」升級，計劃包圍政總。開始學聯在集會中，宣布將運動升級，前往包圍禮賓府。其後示威者重新佔領龍和道，與警方爆發衝突。過千名示威者沿添美道向龍和道進發，約10時50分龍和道隧道已完全由示威者堵塞，11時學聯表示已包圍政總，呼籲示威者留守。<br />\n<br />\n最高峰時近5,000示威者參與，但警方亟欲重開龍和道，通宵與示威者爆發了四場攻防戰。示威者曾兩度佔領政總外的龍和道，當中大部份都是赤手空拳，只有少數人配備了簡單的頭盔及盾牌自衞，及隨手找來鐵馬及垃圾桶做防線。相反警方以警棍、胡椒噴霧、催淚水劑與水炮鎮壓，民眾堅守12小時後最終節節敗退，有大量市民受傷，警方更一度順勢循添馬公園及政府總部行人天橋攻至海富中心港鐵站口，是佔領局勢穩定以來警方最接近金鐘佔領區核心的一次。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:59:26.000Z","msg":"今時今日唔會再有義士赤手空拳上陣"},{"pid":"d35f68316fa434dffcaca4ed765681c85f32b6e6","tid":1520673,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:59:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be8b817b24f0822c251cbcbc6de593bfff55c275","tid":1520673,"uid":1102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:00:11.000Z","msg":"不被捕不受傷"},{"pid":"afa7d8d2f4383d25d55eeb2e2a96473b8825e91b","tid":1520673,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:06:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gi