b6412d47e","tid":1520673,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T02:24:04.000Z","msg":"政府目標得一個 盡快清場<br />\n政府琴日已經按捺不住 要拉一班立法會議員<br />\n目標係引示威者All In<br />\n<br />\n參考返2014年11月30日<br />\n雨傘end game 主動送頭<br />\n最後士氣一沉不起<br />\n今日831 大量風向吹緊一家要去西環<br />\n老老豆豆 去琴西環就贏咩<br />\n要做 香港大把地方要做<br />\n<br />\n總之 唔好去西環<br />\n<br />\n「雨傘革命之學聯升級」發生於2014年11月30日，學民思潮及學聯宣布希望包圍政府總部阻礙政府運作，以將行動升級。示威者與警方星夜於龍和道一帶展開攻防戰，惟至早上節節敗退，警方一度攻至海富中心港鐵站口，是佔領局勢穩定以來警方最接近金鐘佔領區核心的一次。學聯升級行動全面失敗，更有大量市民受傷，網民對相關策略及警方的舉動議論紛紛。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:19:47.000Z","msg":"正苦叫去西環，偏偏唔去，去宗教集會！"},{"pid":"3ae6b0d4762ebef8e076e912d88cd88a183b77ea","tid":1520673,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:21:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"de87e6ebf6c8340e2b88fba848bec740dfeadb63","tid":1520673,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:23:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f236ca0e5c293d2059df89404649e8c21c51ee4","tid":1520673,"uid":59804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:24:04.000Z","msg":"西環最新交通消息（11：06）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1520799\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1520799</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"84a13c80b6d48c6a75b85223574b193fcb069050","tid":1520673,"uid":186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:29:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a739e6abbbd8a2a6ae36259bf7a1bf79ebdbfe4c","tid":1520673,"uid":179649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:30:10.000Z","msg":"g持行街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5304ea1400f089abb8e917ea2652042453994fd0","tid":1520673,"uid":186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T03:35:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https